quran[67]{c,v,t}:
  90,1,Nditsuba khulitokho lino
  90,2,Ne ewe oli omwibule welitokho lino
  90,3,Nende khumwibusi nende shiayebula
  90,4,Toto bwene khwaloonga omundu khubusandi
  90,5,Aparanga mbu abulaho omundu yesi yesi umunyala
  90,6,"aboola mbu: ndasamba eshiachi shomwandu"
  90,7,Kho aparanga mbu abulaho yesiyesi umulolanga
  90,8,Koo shikhwamuhelesia tsimoni tsibili
  90,9,Nende olulimi nebinwa bibili
  90,10,Ne nikhumumanyia tsinjila tsiosi tsibili
  90,11,Ne shiyeruma khunjila yebisikirasio yeshisia tawe
  90,12,Ne nishina shikhwechesia okhumanya injila yebisikirasio yeshisia
  90,13,Okhuhabina omusumba(omurumwa)
  90,14,nohomba okhulisia inyanga yeyinzala
  90,15,Omufwilwa omwikho
  90,16,nohomba omumanani omushisandu
  90,17,Mana abe mubalia basuubila nibatinyisania okhwifwila ne nibaboolelana okhulolanila eshisa
  90,18,Abo nibo Abandu bomukhono musaatsa
  90,19,"Ne balia bakhaya ebimanyiso biefu, abo nibo Abandu bomukhono mukhasi"
  90,20,Omulilo omululu kwabotokhana buli tsimbeka
  91,1,Nditsuba khuliuba nende obulafu bwalio
  91,2,"Nende\tkhumwesi\tshingala kuliloondanga"
  91,3,Nende khushitere olwashiliretsanga habulafu
  91,4,Nende eshilo olwa shifunikhanga
  91,5,"Nende\tkhulikulu\tnende\tulia waliumbakha"
  91,6,Nende khuliloba nende ulia walikwalasia
  91,7,"Nende\tkhu mwoyo nende ulia wakuleng’aasia"
  91,8,Mana nakumanyisia injila yamabii nende yamalayi. 15. Naye sharitsanga karulilaho tawe
  91,9,toto bwene yamala okhubura ulwa wakutswenula
  91,10,Ne toto bwene yamala okhusikha ulia wakulekhula
  91,11,babu Tsamudi bayingasia (omurumwa wabu) khulwo okhubeela obufuru bwabu
  91,12,ulwa yanguya womwoyo omumu mubo
  91,13,"aho Omurumwa wa Nyasaye nababoolela mbu ; ingamia ino ni ya Nyasaye, muyileshe inywe amatsi kayio ne mulayira tawe"
  91,14,"Mana bamala bamuyingasia nibaiyira, khulwako Nyasaye wabu nabasishia khulwo khubeela tsimbi tsiabu nabamala boosi"
  91,15,Naye sharitsanga karulilaho tawe
  92,1,Nditsuba khu shilo olwashifunikhanga
  92,2,Nende olwe eshiteere shilolekhanga
  92,3,"Nende\tkhuwaloonga\teshisatsa neshikhasi"
  92,4,Toto bwene okhukhalabana khwenyu khukabukhana
  92,5,Ne ulia urusia mana arie Omuloonji
  92,6,Mana nakhola kali amalayi
  92,7,Khwitsa okhumuwanguyisilia kabe amangu
  92,8,"Ne ulia ukhola obwimani, mana abule oluchendo na bashie"
  92,9,Mana nafuukula amalayi
  92,10,Khwitsa okhumuwanguyisilia kabe amasiro
  92,11,Ne omwandu kukwe kulimukhonya shina olwa aliba nasikhanga
  92,12,Toto bwene kali khu efwe okhwechesia obulunjifu
  92,13,Ne toto bwene kali khu efwe ka mutsuli (akhera) nende kokhuranjilila
  92,14,"Kho\tebekanyisilia\tkhumulilo kwakhanga"
  92,15,Shali kwinjilamwo halali ulia Omubii muno
  92,16,Ulia wafuukula mana nafutarira omukongo
  92,17,Ne ulia waria Nyasaye alireebwa ehale ninakwo
  92,18,ulia Urusinjia omwandu kukwe khulwo khwitswenula
  92,19,Ne shikali mbu aliho yesi yesi wamukholela amalayi lano khamurunje
  92,20,Halali nokhukhaaba obulekhule bwa Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi Owoluyali
  92,21,Naye yakhachame
  93,1,Nditsuba khu isenya
  93,2,Nditsuba khushilo olwa shinjilanga
  93,3,"Nyasaye wuwo shiyakhulekha tawe, nohomba shiyakhusinyishila tawe"
  93,4,Ne imbeli itsanga ilaba indayi okhushila ebise biaranjilila
  93,5,Ne Nyasaye wuwo omulesi alakhuwa okhula ochame
  93,6,Shiyakhunyoola noli omufwilwa ya khuwa eshimenyo
  93,7,Ne yakhunyoola niwakora yakhulunjisia
  93,8,"Nenakhunyoola\tnoli\tomumanani nakhuyindiasia"
  93,9,Mana omufwilwa olamuyindushila tawe
  93,10,Naye usaba olamuwusa tawe
  93,11,Ne obwokholo bwa Nyasaye wuwo omulesi obuboole